Before 0.9.8 release
--------------------

- Make UserTransactionImpl serializable by looking up
  the transaction domain upon de-serialization.

- Need to validate that both TransactionManager and TransactionFactory
  provide the proper timeout in seconds.

- Clock API will change to be fully singleton pattern and match new names used in Tyrex configuration file

- Allow ResourceLimits to be obtained and changed from Resource object

- tryLock() method for LockSet

- Auto-recover option to domain configuration file


Under consideration for version 0.9.9
-------------------------------------

- Add ThreadPool implementation with ThreadPoolMetrics for statistics (including average
  execution time, average block time, block/unblock ratio)

- ThreadPool to use Runnable but add stop() method

- Have all asynch transactions complete in background thread of TransactionDomain

